---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import pic1 from "../assets/images/vietnam.png";
import Collage from "./Collage.astro";
---

<section>
  <h1>ABOUT ME</h1>
</section>
<section class="flex">
  <div>
    <p>
      At 27 years old, I am a passionate and creative individual with a
      background in multimedia design. I firmly believe in the motto, "See good
      in all things," which guides my approach to life and work.<br />
      <br /> Originally from Copenhagen, I recently relocated to Horsens, where my
      partner and I have settled into our new home. We share our space with Mocca,
      our delightful Bernese Mountain Dog, who has quickly become a beloved member
      of the family. <br />
      <br />In my free time, I find joy in simple pleasures like reading,
      photography, and long walks. These activities not only help me unwind but
      also fuel my creativity and allow me to see the world from different
      perspectives. I also cherish moments spent with family and friends, as
      they are an essential part of my life. <br />
      <br /> My journey from Copenhagen to Horsens represents more than just a change
      of scenery; it's a new chapter filled with opportunities to grow personally
      and professionally while embracing all the beauty life has to offer.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <Collage />
  </div>
</section>

